    <div id="titleDidYouKnow" class="article">
    <span class=rightcornerlink >
            <a href="/register/login?why=edit&ref_=tt_trv_trv"
rel="login">Edit</a>
    </span>
        <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
    <div id="trivia" class="txt-block">
        <h4>Trivia</h4>
The role of Jon's brother, Peter, was intended for <a href="/name/nm0586568?ref_=tt_trv_trv">Mads Mikkelsen</a>'s brother, <a href="/name/nm0586565?ref_=tt_trv_trv">Lars Mikkelsen</a>. When he dropped out, Mads Mikkelsen suggested <a href="/name/nm0675409?ref_=tt_trv_trv">Mikael Persbrandt</a> to replace him.        <a href="trivia?ref_=tt_trv_trv"
class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>
                <hr />
     <div id="goofs"  class="txt-block">
        <h4>Goofs</h4>
Set in 1871, lever action rifles available would be the model 1866 Winchester or 1860 Henry, but the weapon on screen has a loading gate which eliminates the Henry, making it a Winchester. It lacks the brass receiver of the 1866 yellow boy, indicating the continuity editors and property master substituted a later model Winchester.        <a href="trivia?tab=gf&ref_=tt_trv_gf"
class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>   
                <hr />
    <div id="quotes" class="text-block">
        <h4>Quotes</h4>
<a href="/name/nm0675409/?ref_=tt_trv_qu"
><span class="character">Peter</span></a>:
Yeah, I was a soldier once, and it taught me a lesson. Don't get into a fight you know you're gonna lose.
<br /><a href="/name/nm0584206/?ref_=tt_trv_qu"
><span class="character">Lester</span></a>:
[<span class="fine">under his breath</span>]
Cowards.
<br />        <a href="trivia?tab=qt&ref_=tt_trv_qu"
class="nobr" >See more</a> &raquo;
    </div>
                <hr />
    <div id="connections" class="text-block">
        <h4>Connections</h4>
        References <a href="/title/tt0044706?ref_=tt_trv_cnn">High Noon</a>&nbsp;(1952)


        <a href="trivia?tab=mc&ref_=tt_trv_cnn"
class="nobr" >See more</a> &raquo;
    </div>
